://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2324-TW</a>)</p></section><section><p>4. 投信累計買超 2 日的股票<br/>第一金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2892:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2892\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2892-TW</a>)、台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、光寶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2301-TW</a>)、仁寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2324-TW</a>)</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>5. 投信當日 (31) 買超的股票<br/>第一金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2892:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2892\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2892-TW</a>)、台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、光寶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2301-TW</a>)、元大金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2885:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2885\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2885-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
